description:
Air Wick Odour Neutralising Spray is an air freshener that neutralises bad smells and freshens up your home.

Air Wick Odour Neutralising Spray is a household, trigger pump spray air freshener. It is free from propellants and dyes and neutralises bad smells, freshening up your home. The fragrance is infused with essential oils to provide a wonderful and invigorating fragrance experience.

Refreshing notes of eucalyptus are combined with the sweet aroma of freesias for a revitalising atmosphere.

Neutralises bad smells and freshens up your home.

Free from propellants

Free from dyes

Fragrance infused with Essential Oils

Eucalyptus & Freesia fragrance
name: Airwick Odour Neutralising Spray Eucalyptus & Freesia 236ml
